The Umeboshi-Kaname notetype styling and card templates are derived
from the AnKing Note Types project. The original work can be found at:

  https://github.com/AnKing-VIP/AnKing-Note-Types

Modifications include:
- Japanese language support with furigana (ruby) annotations
- ClaudeFlare cloud sync integration
- Cloze one-by-one reveal system
- LLM-powered Q&A chat interface
- Brain rest countdown overlay
- Custom font loading (Noto Sans JP, Open Sans, M PLUS 1 Code)

